&lt;p&gt;Make it TOGETHER – We work as one, respecting each voice and tapping into our unique strengths across teams—so we can solve problems in new ways.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Make it RIGHT – We hold ourselves to a high standard of excellence,&amp;nbsp;fulfilling our commitments to the customer, their patients, and our team members.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Make it COUNT – We take pride in our day-to-day work, knowing the impact we make – taking on challenges big and small to improve patient health.&lt;/p&gt;
